data.description: 4 bedrooms and 3 1/2 baths on the east side of town! This beautiful two story home in Dobbs Glen has everything you've been looking for. The large eat in kitchen has tons of natural light and is great for entertaining. It has recently been updated with new appliances, countertops and floors. The main level also features a formal dining room and an office as well as a family room with a gas fireplace. The backyard has a nice deck and is fully fenced. Upstairs has a very large master suite with a walk in closet and en-suite bathroom. Two more bedrooms share a jack and Jill bath, and there is a 4th bedroom that also has an en-suite bathroom! There's even a bonus room over the two car garage. This home has so much room! The roof is only one year old and the HVAC is less than 2 years old. Dobbs and Deming park and all the shopping the east side has to offer are just minutes away.
